Initial Table
We can quickly convert this into gt table like so. Look pretty good, and the player headshots look fine as well.


skater_game_score %>% 
  slice(1:10) %>%
  select(player, headshot_url, games:pts)%>% 
  gt() %>% 
  text_transform(
    locations = cells_body(vars(headshot_url)),
